 biographical sketch:




  scott b.  baden received his bs in electrical engineering from 
   duke university
  in 1978 and his
  ph.d. in  computer science  from 
   uc berkeley  in 1987. after spending two
  years as a post-doc at  
  lawrence berkeley laboratry, and a year traveling the globe,
  he joined the 
   department of
  computer science and engineering  at
   ucsd  in 1990.  he is also
 senior fellow at the   
 san diego supercomputer center. 








